text: Brandon Roberto Palacios Bustamante (born 26 March 1998) is a Peruvian footballer who plays as a right winger for Peruvian Primera División side Cusco FC. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Living people Category:Peruvian footballers Category:1998 births Category:Sporting Cristal footballers Category:Universidad Técnica de Cajamarca footballers Category:Universidad San Martín footballers Category:Cusco FC footballers Category:Peruvian Primera División players Category:Association football midfielders
